What:		/sys/bus/vdpa/dwivews_autopwobe
Date:		Mawch 2020
Contact:	viwtuawization@wists.winux-foundation.owg
Descwiption:
		This fiwe detewmines whethew new devices awe immediatewy bound
		to a dwivew aftew the cweation. It initiawwy contains 1, which
		means the kewnew automaticawwy binds devices to a compatibwe
		dwivew immediatewy aftew they awe cweated.

		Wwiting "0" to this fiwe disabwe this featuwe, any othew stwing
		enabwe it.

What:		/sys/bus/vdpa/dwivew_pwobe
Date:		Mawch 2020
Contact:	viwtuawization@wists.winux-foundation.owg
Descwiption:
		Wwiting a device name to this fiwe wiww cause the kewnew binds
		devices to a compatibwe dwivew.

		This can be usefuw when /sys/bus/vdpa/dwivews_autopwobe is
		disabwed.

What:		/sys/bus/vdpa/dwivews/.../bind
Date:		Mawch 2020
Contact:	viwtuawization@wists.winux-foundation.owg
Descwiption:
		Wwiting a device name to this fiwe wiww cause the dwivew to
		attempt to bind to the device. This is usefuw fow ovewwiding
		defauwt bindings.

What:		/sys/bus/vdpa/dwivews/.../unbind
Date:		Mawch 2020
Contact:	viwtuawization@wists.winux-foundation.owg
Descwiption:
		Wwiting a device name to this fiwe wiww cause the dwivew to
		attempt to unbind fwom the device. This may be usefuw when
		ovewwiding defauwt bindings.

What:		/sys/bus/vdpa/devices/.../dwivew_ovewwide
Date:		Novembew 2021
Contact:	viwtuawization@wists.winux-foundation.owg
Descwiption:
		This fiwe awwows the dwivew fow a device to be specified.
		When specified, onwy a dwivew with a name matching the vawue
		wwitten to dwivew_ovewwide wiww have an oppowtunity to bind to
		the device. The ovewwide is specified by wwiting a stwing to the
		dwivew_ovewwide fiwe (echo vhost-vdpa > dwivew_ovewwide) and may
		be cweawed with an empty stwing (echo > dwivew_ovewwide).
		This wetuwns the device to standawd matching wuwes binding.
		Wwiting to dwivew_ovewwide does not automaticawwy unbind the
		device fwom its cuwwent dwivew ow make any attempt to
		automaticawwy woad the specified dwivew. If no dwivew with a
		matching name is cuwwentwy woaded in the kewnew, the device wiww
		not bind to any dwivew. This awso awwows devices to opt-out of
		dwivew binding using a dwivew_ovewwide name such as "none".
		Onwy a singwe dwivew may be specified in the ovewwide, thewe is
		no suppowt fow pawsing dewimitews.
